  "title": "Energizing Sunrise Smoothie Bowl",
  "description": "A vibrant smoothie bowl blending mixed berries, mango, banana, and spinach with almond milk and chia seeds. Quick to assemble and packed with fruit and fiber for a refreshing breakfast.",
  "ingredients": [
    "1 cup mixed berries (strawberries, raspberries, blueberries)",
    "1/2 cup mango chunks",
    "1/2 cup spinach leaves",
    "1 banana",
    "1/2 cup unsweetened almond milk",
    "1 tbsp chia seeds",
    "1 tbsp honey (optional)"
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "In a blender, combine the mixed berries, mango chunks, spinach leaves, and banana. Blend until smooth.",
    "Pour the blended mixture into a bowl.",
    "Stir in the chia seeds and honey (if using).",
    "Top with your favorite fresh fruits or nuts for added crunch and flavor."
  ],
